divs: Sighting DetailsI saw the object outside at about 7pm. Above it was another object that I had been seeing for several days. I took pictures of them from the same spot on my deck at various times during the sighting. They move west and descend as they normally do (these sightings have been occurring since lat Jan.) One lower object was gone at about 9. The higher elevated one was gone about 9:15pm.
